OL,3,CMay Day talks to take place in bid to
OL,4,Cresolve Birmingham bin strike
OL,6,FCrucial talks aimed at resolving the
OL,7,Flong-running Birmingham bin strike are
OL,8,Fto take place on Thursday morning.
OL,10,FThe general secretary of the Unite
OL,11,Funion, Sharon Graham, will lead the
OL,12,FMay Day discussions under the auspices
OL,13,Fof conciliation service Acas.
OL,15,FLast week, Unite said it believed a
OL,16,Fdeal to end the industrial action
OL,17,Fcould be "within touching distance".
