OL,6,FBut a row flared on Tuesday when the
OL,7,Funion accused Birmingham City Council
OL,8,Fof planning to cut the pay of bin
OL,9,Florry drivers by up to #8,000.
OL,11,FThe council insisted it is carrying
OL,12,Fout a "fair and transparent" job
OL,13,Fevaluation process, jointly agreed
OL,14,Fwith trade unions, to ensure it
OL,15,Fcomplies with equal pay laws.
OL,17,FMs Graham said: "Unite will not stand
OL,18,Fby and allow the council to inflict
OL,19,Fthese savage pay cuts on workers. It
OL,20,Fwill not be accepted.
