OL,3,CMay Day talks to take place in bid to
OL,4,Cresolve Birmingham bin strike
OL,6,FLast week, it was announced that the
OL,7,Fcity council's bin boss, the executive
OL,8,Fdirector of city operations Craig
OL,9,FCooper, will be leaving his role in
OL,10,FJune and a search for his replacement
OL,11,Fwill begin "immediately".
OL,13,FRichard Brooks, who the council says
OL,14,Fhas worked closely with Mr Cooper
OL,15,Fduring the bin strike in the city
OL,16,Foperations department, will take over
OL,17,Fthe role on an interim basis.
